Source: ros-hydro-master-discovery-fkie
Section: misc
Priority: extra
Maintainer: Alexander Tiderko <alexander.tiderko@gmail.com>
Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 7.0.50~), ros-hydro-catkin, ros-hydro-multimaster-msgs-fkie
Homepage: http://ros.org/wiki/master_discovery_fkie
Standards-Version: 3.9.2

Package: ros-hydro-master-discovery-fkie
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, avahi-daemon, python-avahi, ros-hydro-multimaster-msgs-fkie, ros-hydro-rosgraph, ros-hydro-roslib, ros-hydro-rospy
Description: A Node to discovery the running ROS Masters in local network. The discovering is done by send a echo heartbeat messages to a defined multicast group. The alternative is to use a zeroconf/avahi daemon to register the ROS master as service and discover other ROS masters.
